OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome sunny
OL,6,Fspells to start the evening, but
OL,7,Fbecoming increasingly cloudy, with
OL,8,Fshowers moving in from the northwest.
OL,9,FShowers may merge into longer spells
OL,10,Fof rain overnight, becoming
OL,11,Foccasionally heavy with a low risk of
OL,12,Fthunder.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FA mixture of sunny spells and
OL,15,Fblustery showers on Tuesday, with a
OL,16,Frisk of hail and thunder. Feeling cool
OL,17,Ffor the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
